Create request
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/requests \
 -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
 -d '{
"employeeName": "Nathan",
"startDate": "2026-06-01",
"endDate": "2026-06-05",
"reason": "Vacation"
}'

Get all requests
curl http://localhost:3000/requests

Approve request
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/requests/1 \
 -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
 -d '{"status":"approve"}'
